title: Bug 23267[Import/Export] Import Project should have a default folder
description: Bug 23267[Import/Export] Import Project should have a default folder
OB: When importing an existing Eclipse project on XP and clicking the Browse button, the dialog does not have a good default folder.
EB: The Import Project feature should provide a default folder in the dialog when importing an existing Eclipse project on XP and clicking the Browse button.
SR: Provide a default folder in the dialog when importing an existing Eclipse project on XP and clicking the Browse button during the Import Project process.
